<section class="section" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem__layout">

      <div class="problem__left reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why this matters</p>
        <h2 id="problem-heading">
          LinkedIn is your highest-value B2B channel.<br />
          <span class="problem__muted">Most companies are wasting it.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem__right">
        <p class="problem__lead reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Over 65 million decision-makers are active on LinkedIn. Four out of five LinkedIn members
          drive business decisions. B2B marketers consistently rate it as their strongest channel
          for lead generation, thought leadership, and brand awareness.
        </p>
        <p class="problem__body reveal reveal-delay-2">
          And yet — company pages go weeks without a post. Executive profiles read like old CVs.
          Ad budgets burn through audiences with no clear targeting strategy. Content gets published
          without a plan and earns nothing.
        </p>
        <p class="problem__close reveal reveal-delay-3">
          The gap between what LinkedIn can deliver and what most companies actually get from it
          is significant. <strong>Closing that gap is what we do.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .problem__muted {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .problem__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .problem__body {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .problem__close {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .problem__close strong {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .problem__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-10); }
  }
</style>
